    <title><![CDATA[Asian stocks slip as investors await U.S., Chinese data]]></title>
    <link>http://www.ctvnews.ca/business/asian-stocks-slip-as-investors-await-u-s-chinese-data-1.2900472</link>
    <description><![CDATA[Most Asian stock markets headed lower on Friday as investors evaluated the latest set of corporate earnings and awaited a slew of U.S. and Chinese economic data.]]></description>

    <title><![CDATA[Competition Bureau approves Lowe's $3.2B takeover of Rona]]></title>
    <link>http://www.ctvnews.ca/business/competition-bureau-approves-lowe-s-3-2b-takeover-of-rona-1.2899894</link>
    <description><![CDATA[The Competition Bureau has approved the Lowe's takeover of Quebec-based Rona. The federal agency says it has concluded the acquisition by the U.S. company won't limit consumer choice.]]></description>

              <item>
    <title><![CDATA[Quebec unveils bill regulating taxis, Uber]]></title>
    <link>http://www.ctvnews.ca/business/quebec-unveils-bill-regulating-taxis-uber-1.2899512</link>
    <description><![CDATA[It's up to Uber to conform to Quebec laws regulating the taxi industry and not the other way around, the province's transport minister said Thursday, as he tabled legislation that would create a single legal framework to encompass taxi companies and the popular ride-hailing app alike.]]></description>
    <author></author>

(Ryan Remiorz / THE CANADIAN PRESS)]]></enclosure>

    <title><![CDATA[World economy growth is flat-lining: UN report]]></title>

    <title><![CDATA[McDonald's tests fresh beef at 14 U.S. restaurants]]></title>
    <link>http://www.ctvnews.ca/business/mcdonald-s-tests-fresh-beef-at-14-u-s-restaurants-1.2899676</link>
    <description><![CDATA[McDonald's says it's testing fresh beef at 14 restaurants in Dallas, but says it's too early to say whether fresh beef could replace its frozen patties nationally.]]></description>

    <title><![CDATA[Mulroney implies Peladeau's eventual return to Quebecor is inevitable]]></title>
    <link>http://www.ctvnews.ca/business/mulroney-implies-peladeau-s-eventual-return-to-quebecor-is-inevitable-1.2899391</link>
    <description><![CDATA[Although there are no immediate plans for Pierre Karl Peladeau to return to a decision-making role at Quebecor Inc., chairman Brian Mulroney implied Thursday it is just a matter of time before he comes back in some capacity.]]></description>

    <title><![CDATA[Canadian Tire goes back to the future with innovative new print catalogue]]></title>
    <link>http://www.ctvnews.ca/business/canadian-tire-goes-back-to-the-future-with-innovative-new-print-catalogue-1.2899748</link>

    <title><![CDATA[Nations make anti-corruption vows, but hard action varies]]></title>
    <link>http://www.ctvnews.ca/business/nations-make-anti-corruption-vows-but-hard-action-varies-1.2898752</link>
    <description><![CDATA[A handful of countries agreed Thursday to publish lists of who really owns companies in their territories, a move hailed by the British government as a step toward stopping a global plague of tax evasion, money-laundering and bribery.]]></description>
